00:00:52.430 --> 00:00:53.130
Fine.

00:00:53.130 --> 00:00:55.260
You're definitely on
for asking a question.

00:00:55.260 --> 00:00:59.150
But many of us are fascinated
by what's been going on,

00:00:59.150 --> 00:01:01.690
and have been incredibly
excited to live through,

00:01:01.690 --> 00:01:03.930
vicariously, this
historical event

00:01:03.930 --> 00:01:06.110
