I remember once I
was a grad student,

00:07:45.190 --> 00:07:47.430
and a fellow grad
student of mine

00:07:47.430 --> 00:07:50.690
was lamenting about how
challenging theoretical physics

00:07:50.690 --> 00:07:51.190
was.

