00:35:14.176 --> 00:35:16.170
-Coffee is a very
serious business

00:35:16.170 --> 00:35:18.630
in the life of a theorist.

00:35:18.630 --> 00:35:23.370
It's not like physics research
where you can wait for 30 years

00:35:23.370 --> 00:35:27.365
before you know
if you are right.

00:35:27.365 --> 00:35:31.010
Within a few
minutes it pays off.

00:35:31.010 --> 00:35:35.170
If you succeed, it's great.

00:35:35.170 --> 00:35:40.170
If you fail, you get to try
another one in another minute.

00:35:40.170 --> 00:35:44.100
In particle physics,
you construct the theory

00:35:44.100 --> 00:35:47.940
20 years ago, and it
may take that long

00:35:47.940 --> 00:35:51.410
before you know if you're
on the right track.

00:35:51.410 --> 00:35:56.140
Jumping from failure to failure
with undiminished enthusiasm

00:35:56.140 --> 00:35:59.561
is the big secret to success.

00:35:59.561 --> 00:36:03.330
