the next generation machine

00:49:28.670 --> 00:49:31.260
to just push the energy
frontier a little bit,

00:49:31.260 --> 00:49:35.090
you're talking about another
20 years' investment.

00:49:35.090 --> 00:49:38.880
So it actually makes perfect
sense that it took so long.

